<p><font color="#FF0000">&gt;&gt;&gt;</font>One Saturday I got call
from a couple traveling from Washington to Mexico. Their throw out
bearing disintegrated because the return spring on the tranny gave
out. They told me that some guy in San Francisco had given them a
